    <h1>Categories</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Categories help you group your products.
How do you want to structure your items in the plentyShop?
Which merchandise groups match your product catalogue?</p>
</div>
<h3 id="_procedure" class="discrete">Procedure</h3>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><a href="/en/item/settings/categories#100">Sketch a category structure</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="/en/item/settings/categories#200">Create the necessary categories and sub-categories</a></p>
</li>
